TurboClearsilver is a plugin for TurboGears that provides support for the 
Clearsilver templating language.

Clearsilver is a templating language written in C that provides good separation
between display and logic

TurboClearsilver uses a wonderful piece of code from the Trac project (http://projects.edgewall.com/trac).  It is copyright Edgewall Software and is subject to the license found in the COPYING file.

The rest of the code is under the MIT License which can be found in the LICENSE file.
